  • Packages that use IDictionaryVisitable 
    Package Description
    org.ensor.data.atom
    This package holds objects which represent abstract data which can be serialized.
    org.ensor.data.atom.json
    This package contains serializers to convert the Dictionary and List structures into JSON and back again.
    org.ensor.data.atom.xml
    This package contains a serialzier for writing the dictionary and list objects to XML documents and reading them back again.
